      <title>“华尔街鳄鱼”因加密货币案被判处 18 个月监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/hacker-s-wife-razzlekhan-gets-18-months-for-money-laundering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这位在说唱视频中自称“华尔街鳄鱼”和“Razzlekhan”的女子因帮助其黑客丈夫清洗从 Bitfinex 交易所窃取的加密货币而被判入狱 18 个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/hacker-s-wife-razzlekhan-gets-18-months-for-money-laundering</guid>
